name: Capital Group World Bond Select ETFTM (Canada)
longDescription: Fund will invest at least 80% of its assets in bonds and other debt securities, taken at market value at the time of acquisition, which may be represented by other investment instruments, including derivatives.
fulldescription: Fund will invest at least 80% of its assets in bonds and other debt securities, taken at market value at the time of acquisition, which may be represented by other investment instruments, including derivatives.
